data.meta_description: Salome von Berg-Schelklingen was born between 1093 and 1101 in Berg Castle, daughter of Heinrich Graf von Berg-Schelklingen and Adelheid von Vohburg. She was married about March 1115 to Bolesław III Krzywousty Piast, they gave birth to 1 child. She died on July 27, 1144. This information is part of maximum test by Ard van Bergen on Genealogy Online.
